title: Patriots activate WR Brandon LaFell from PUP list
text:
Home » News » Sports » NFL » Patriots activate WR Brandon… Patriots activate WR Brandon LaFell from PUP list By The Associated Press October 24, 2015 5:12 pm 
FOXBOROUGH, Mass. (AP) — The New England Patriots have added receiver Brandon LaFell to the 53-man roster in time for Sunday’s game against the New York Jets. 
LaFell had been on the reserve/physically unable to perform list since Sept. 5 with a foot injury. 
LaFell had a career-high 74 receptions, 953 yards and seven touchdowns last season. He added 13 receptions for 199 yards and two touchdowns in the postseason. Topics:
